      <p class="entry-actions">
        
        <span class="squarespace-social-buttons inline-style" data-system-data-id="1642039380116-YLLU8ULGZ1JX5MRDYNZA" data-asset-url="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/565c1ab5e4b05079e4bfa169/1642039380116-YLLU8ULGZ1JX5MRDYNZA/City+Boy+Self+Titled+Album+Cover.jpg" data-record-type="1" data-full-url="/musicblog/city-boy-self-titled-album-review" data-title="City Boy – Self-Titled (Album Review)"></span>
