      <a href="/musicblog/meat-loaf-hang-cool-teddy-bear-album-review"><div class="main-image content-fill"><img data-src="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/565c1ab5e4b05079e4bfa169/1635723034112-5SSIV8TYHQSPZE3GA0RM/Meat+Loaf+Hang+Cool+Teddy+Bear+Album+Cover.jpg" data-image="https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/565c1ab5e4b05079e4bfa169/1635723034112-5SSIV8TYHQSPZE3GA0RM/Meat+Loaf+Hang+Cool+Teddy+Bear+Album+Cover.jpg" data-image-dimensions="2500x2500" data-image-focal-point="0.5,0.292" alt="Meat Loaf – Hang Cool Teddy Bear (Album Review)"  /></div></a>
