  <article class="entry cf hentry category-rfs-du-sol category-electronic category-2020s tag-rfs-du-sol tag-surrender tag-next-to-me tag-make-it-happen tag-see-you-again tag-i-dont-wanna-leave tag-alive tag-alive-reprise tag-on-my-knees tag-wildfire tag-devotion tag-always author-mark-greentree post-type-text article-index-7" id="article-61762bcc82bc6837a0b1eee0" data-item-id="61762bcc82bc6837a0b1eee0">

  
    <div class="main-image-wrapper">
